<header>
<div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center p-3 px-md-4 mb-3 bg-white border-bottom box-shadow">
      <h5 class="my-0 mr-md-auto font-weight-normal">Task management system</h5>
      <nav class="my-2 my-md-0 mr-md-3">
        <span class="p-2 text-dark" ><%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %></span>
        <span class="p-2 text-dark" ><%= link_to "Sign In", signin_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %></span>
        <span class="p-2 text-dark" ><%= link_to "Sign Out", signout_path, class: " btn btn-outline-primary" %></span>
      </nav>
</div>
</header>
<body>
<div class="pricing-header px-3 py-3 pt-md-5 pb-md-4 mx-auto text-center">
  <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to  task management system!</h1>
  <p class="lead">Do you want to create a task management system for yourself? Then sign up or sign into your account and create your own tasks. You will be able to specify the due date and select the priority of the task.</p>
  <br>
   <nav class="my-2 my-md-0 mr-md-3">
    <% if current_user %>
  Signed in as <%= current_user.email %>.
    <span class="p-2 text-black"><%= link_to "Sign Out", signout_path,  class: "btn btn-primary" %></span>
  <% else %>
    <span class="p-2 text-black"><%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path,  class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %> </span>
    <span class="p-2 text-black"><%= link_to "Sign In", signin_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></span>
  <% end %>
   </nav>
</div>
</body>
